hackathon-description-text: HackRiddle is Embry-Riddle's first ever hackathon hosted on campus! It will be 12 hours long and will include a lot of fun, prizes, coding, food, and swag!
hackathon-location-google-maps: https://maps.google.com/?q=600 S Clyde Morris Blvd, Daytona Beach, FL 32114, USA

hackathon-judging-criteria.judging-criterion: Judges will walk around during the expo and pick their favorite projects. Judges come from a variety of backgrounds — engineering, design, business, social impact, and more. Each team will be judged by at least two judges.
